title: Air Canada Brisbane-Vancouver flights to start in 2016
text:
Air Canada Brisbane-Vancouver flights... Air Canada Brisbane-Vancouver flights to start in 2016 2 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
In a blow to the airport, Malaysia Airlines last month announced it would axe its Brisbane-Kuala Lumpur route in August . But that disappointment was somewhat offset by Air Canada's announcement on Thursday that it would introduce direct trans-Pacific routes between Brisbane and Vancouver next year.   Sydney Morning Herald.
